FROM title t, movie_companies mc, cast_info ci
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year  =  2009 AND mc.company_id  <  124594 AND ci.person_id  <  1238237 AND ci.role_id  >  1
